protected static class BinaryTree.AgeData<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.util.Comparator
implements Serializable and Comparator interfaces. this class stores age(data) and number of people of that ages(numberOfPeople) every AgeData connects each other with left or right reference
